---
layout: base.njk
---
<article>
  <header style="margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8f4f0;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.6; color: #222; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">{{ title }}</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #888;">{{ date | dateJP }}</p>
  </header>
  <div class="post-body" style="font-size: 1rem;">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f0f8f4; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">この記事が参考になったら、ぜひSOELUを試してみてください🍀</p>
    <a href="/" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #888;">← 記事一覧に戻る</a>
  </div>
</article>
<style>
  .post-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #2d7a5f;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e8f4f0;
  }
  .post-body h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #333;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
  }
  .post-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .post-body ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .post-body li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .post-body hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e8f4f0; margin: 2rem 0; }
</style>
